title: Average Duration (in Quarters) from Business Application to Formation within 8 Quarters for New York (DISCONTINUED)
notes:
The Business Formation Statistics are now released on a monthly basis, and the quarterly series will no longer be updated. See BFDUR8QTOTALNSANY (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BFDUR8QTOTALNSANY) for an alternative.

A measure of delay between business application and formation, similar to https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/DUR4QNSANY. The difference is that the window for business formation is restricted to eight quarters, rather than four. The series span the same period as https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BF8QNSANY.
